      "kind": "content",
      "content": [
        {
          "anchor": "return_value",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Return Value",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "The pasteboard writer object to use for managing the item data. Return "
            },
            {
              "type": "codeVoice",
              "code": "nil"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " to prevent the collection view from dragging the item."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "kind": "content",
      "content": [
        {
          "anchor": "discussion",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Discussion",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "The collection view calls this method for each item involved in the drag operation after it has determined that a drag should begin but before the drag operation has started.  Your implementation of this method should create and return the pasteboard writer—an object conforming to the "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nspasteboardwriting"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " protocol—to use for providing the item’s data. Using the object you provide, the collection view creates an "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nsdraggingitem"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " object for you and configures its "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nsdraggingitem/1528559-draggingframe"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " and "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nsdraggingitem/1524302-imagecomponents"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " properties for you using information from the item at the specified index path. "
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "If you implement this method, the collection view does not call the "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nscollectionviewdelegate/1528138-collectionview"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " of your delegate or the "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nscollectionview/1528249-draggingimageforitemsatindexes"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " method of "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": false,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nscollectionview"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "."
            }
          ]
        }
